extends base

block content
  h2 Reset Your Password
  
  p Hello #{firstName},
  
  p We received a request to reset the password for your account. If you didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this email.
  
  p To reset your password, please click the button below:
  
  p(style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;")
    a.btn.btn-primary(href=`${url}`) Reset Password
  
  p This link will expire in 10 minutes for security reasons.
  
  p If the button doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:
  
  p(style="word-break: break-all; color: #3498db;") #{url}
  
  p If you didn't request a password reset, please contact our support team immediately.
  
  p Best regards,
  br
  | The Gideon's Tech Suite Team
